  "name": "EFTPOS Declined error (LINKLY ONILY)",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"eftpos-declined-error-linkly-onily\">EFTPOS Declined error (LINKLY ONILY)</h1>\n<p><span> This guide is for when you receive a <strong>Transaction Declined </strong>prompt immediately after using the PC-EFTPOS button and your <span>EFTPOS is showing</span>  <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> <strong>ONLINE <span>-- </span></strong> </span> for <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkly.com.au%2F\">Linkly </a>connected EFTPOS terminals. </span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"mceclip0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"mceclip0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614123868943/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Please follow the steps below on how to rectify the error.</p>\n<hr></hr><ol><li>Press <strong>Cancel </strong>to close the EFTPOS payment window</li><li><br/><strong>Log out</strong> of POS <span>! IMPORTANT !</span><br/></li><li>Click the <strong>Start</strong><span> </span>menu</li><li>Type <strong>Services</strong><br/></li><li>Open '<strong>Services</strong>'<br/><img id=\"image_1.863876836722233\" src=\"/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 300w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 600w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 800w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 1200w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 1600w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png 2000w, /attachments/token/nJm3Vo5Qwn3NyZyuKldmG8ztR/?name=inline-1813439599.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Find '<strong>Linkly Client</strong>' </li><li>Press '<strong>Restart</strong>'<br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png\" alt=\"mceclip1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4603038208015/mceclip1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/><div>Wait for <strong>Linkly</strong> to turn green</div><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/4614139677199/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Find '<strong>Retail Express Hardware Service</strong>' </li><li>Press '<strong>Restart</strong>'<br/><img id=\"image_2.660125977350263\" src=\"/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png\" alt=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 300w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 600w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 800w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 1200w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 1600w, http://galaxy.maropost.com/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png 2000w, /attachments/token/9JyjDQUowqjSk0wAEwl22GQ8r/?name=inline1920269069.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/></li><li>Log back into <strong>POS</strong><br/></li></ol>",
